'''''Shangani Patrol''''' ni filime y'intambara ishingiye ku gitabo kitari ibihimbano ''A Time to Die'' cyanditswe na Robert Cary (1968)<ref>https://mubi.com/films/shangani-patrol</ref>, hamwe n’amateka ya Shangani Patrol, hamwe na Brian O'Shaughnessy nka Major Allan Wilson na Will Hutchins nk'umuskuti Frederick. Russell Burnham . <ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/389375-shangani-patrol</ref> Harimo n'indirimbo "Shangani Patrol" ya Nick Taylor (recording 1966).<ref>https://www.badmovies.org/forum/index.php?topic=118984.0</ref>

Ku buyobozi bwa Major Wilson, irondo rikurikirana umwami Ndebele Lobengula wahunze hakurya y'uruzi rwa Shangani<ref>https://www.amazon.com/Shangani-Patrol-Simon-Fonthill/dp/0755345622</ref>. Bagabanijwe ku mbaraga nyamukuru, batewe igico na Ndebele impi kandi<ref>https://gwonline.unc.edu/node/6495</ref>, usibye abagabo bake boherejwe nk'imbaraga, bose baricwa<ref>https://hr2.wiki/wiki/Shangani_Patrol_(film)</ref>. Ubwo ni bwo butwari bw'irondo rya Shangani ku buryo Ndebele watsinze yagize ati: "Bari abagabo ariko na ba se bari abagabo mbere yabo<ref>https://rateyourmusic.com/film/shangani_patrol/</ref>." Ukurikije uko umuntu abibona, ibyabaye byari rimwe mu makosa akomeye no kwibeshya kwa gisirikare muri iki gihe cy'amateka, cyangwa igihagararo cyanyuma cyintwari cya bake<ref>https://www.lovingtheclassics.com/pdmovies/shangani-patrol-1970-dvd-r.html</ref>. Ibyabaye byari bifite akamaro gakomeye mubwongereza, Afrika yepfo, na Rodeziya bihwanye na ' Custer's Last stand '. Ngiyo inkuru yabo, yavuzwe muri firime ya 1970 yafatiwe ahitwa Matabeleland, Rhodesia (ubu ni muri [[Zimbabwe]]).<ref>https://bayourenaissanceman.blogspot.com/2020/03/shangani-patrol-movie.html</ref>

